This project will be a simple hello world express app that can be launched
easily in a docker container.

You must have docker installed to run this applciation. You should have nodejs
and npm installed to do development.

To run application enter following commands

npm run docker-build
npm run docker-run

Then point your browser to http://localhost:3000

npm run docker-build - builds the docker image

npm run docker-run - creates a docker container using the docker image